title: Fresca Italia Inc Recalls Pork Products Produced Without Benefit of Import Inspection
summary: WASHINGTON, June 15, 2015 Fresca Italia Inc, a Brisbane, Calif., establishment, is recalling approximately 36 pounds of pork products produced in Italy that were not presented at the U.S. point of entry for inspection, the U.S. Department of Agricultures Food Safety and Inspection Service (FSIS)...
